场景1：单步文本任务(输入文字，返回文字)

前置条件：
  - 系统启动完成
  - 模型X（主）、模型Y（备）已在模型注册中心注册
  - X模型能力标签：["text-generation", "translation"]
  - Y模型能力标签：["text-generation"]

触发事件：
  用户输入纯文本，不包含对图片/视频的生成请求

状态流转：
  READY -> PLANNING（军师Agent解析意图）-> ROUTING（匹配到模型X）-> CALLING（调用模型X）-> SUCCESS
  READY -> ... -> CALLING -> 模型X超时/错误 -> FALLBACK（切换模型Y）-> CALLING -> SUCCESS
  READY -> ... -> FALLBACK -> 模型Y也失败 -> DEAD（不可恢复，终态）

验收标准：
  成功路径：前端收到SUCCESS
    {
        "task_id":"uuid",
        "task_status": "SUCCESS", 
        "system_status":"READY"
        "data": {
            "type":"text",
            "content":"返回的文本内容"}
            }
    
    军师agent返回json保存到日志：
    {
        "task_id":"uuid-xxxx",
        "task_status": "SUCCESS", 
        "system_status":"READY"
        "timestamp":"(保存时间戳)"
        "call_chain": [
            {
                "model_name": "model-x",
                "capability": "text-generation",
                "status": "SUCCESS",
                "attempted_at": "(保存时间戳)"
            }
        ]
    }


  降级路径：模型X失败（超时/401/503），日志记录切换事件，自动调用模型Y，前端收到SUCCESS
    {
        "task_id":"uuid-xx"
        "task_status": "SUCCESS", 
        "system_status":"READY",
        "data": {
            "type":"text",
            "content":"返回的文本内容"}
    }    
    用户无感知,
    
    军师agent返回json保存到日志：
    {
    "task_id":"uuid-xxxx",
    "timestamp":"(保存时间戳)",
    "task_status":"FALLBACK_SUCCESS",
    "system_status":"READY",
    "call_chain":[
        {
            "model_name":"model-x",
            "capability":"text-generation",
            "status"::"FAILED",
            "error_code":xxx,
            "attempted_at":"(保存时间戳)"
            },
        {
            "model_name":"model-y",
            "capability":"text-generation",
            "status"::"SUCCESS",
            "attempted_at":"(保存时间戳)"
        }
    ], //模型降级路线
    "error_summary":"PRIMARY_MODEL_FAILED"
    }


  失败路径：所有模型耗尽，前端收到
   {
        "task_id":"uuid-xxxx",
        "task_status":"FAILED",
        "system_status": "READY", 
        "data": {
            "type":"text",
            "message": "服务暂时不可用，请稍后重试"
            }
    }
    系统日志记录完整调用链和失败码

    军师agent返回json保存到日志：
    {
        "task_id":"uuid-xxxx",
        "timestamp":"(保存时间戳)"
        "task_status":"FAILED"
        "system_status":"READY"
        "call_chain":[
            {
                "model_name":"model-x",
                "capability":"text-generation",
                "status"::"FAILED",
                "error_code":xxx,
                "attempted_at":"(保存时间戳)"
                },
            {
                 "model_name":"model-y",
                "capability":"text-generation",
                "status"::"FAILED",
                "error_code":xxx,
                "attempted_at":"(保存时间戳)"
            }
        ], //模型降级路线
        "error_summary":"ALL_MODEL_FAILED"
    }


